    Click    css=div[class$=option] >> text=${plan_name}    

Fill Start Date 

    Focus   css=input[name=start_date]
    
    ${start_date}     Get Start Date

    Log    ${start_date} 
    
    FOR    ${number}    IN   @{start_date}
        Keyboard Key     press    ${number}
    END

Submmit Enroll Form
